profileText: I'm enthusiastic about diving into new projects, using my skills to create well-maintained user-friendly interfaces that boost businesses' success.
aboutText: I am Goga Ramazashvili, 29 years old with a year-long passion for front-end development. I find joy in taking on interesting projects that not only fuel my passion but also provide opportunities to learn and grow. I love learning new things and aim to apply the latest practices in my work. So let's team up and bring your digital vision to life by embracing the latest innovative techniques.
